92
00:09:29,035 --> 00:09:30,170
Porthos!

93
00:09:30,205 --> 00:09:31,835
Bem, abre-o, Salim.

94
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:36,331
Para de fazer isso e abre o livro, Jamal.

95
00:09:38,435 --> 00:09:39,249
Athos?

96
00:09:58,479 --> 00:10:01,226
Então... Mr. Malik>>

97
00:10:02,610 --> 00:10:04,548
