122
00:11:43,035 --> 00:11:45,965
Idiota estúpido.

123
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:50,000
Fizeste-me perder a merda de um cliente.

124
00:11:50,035 --> 00:11:52,965
O helicóptero do Amitabh!

125
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,235
É o helicóptero do Amitabh!

126
00:11:54,833 --> 00:11:55,705
Amitabh!

127
00:11:57,922 --> 00:12:00,420
Amitabh Bachchan!

128
00:12:16,236 --> 00:12:17,280
Abre, Salim!

129
00:12:58,509 --> 00:13:00,654
Amitabh Bachchan!

130
00:13:17,140 --> 00:13:18,877
Meu senhor Amitabh!

131
00:13:19,629 --> 00:13:21,237
Mexe-te, mexe-te! Sai do caminho!

132
