139
00:14:43,102 --> 00:14:45,330
Mas era meu...>>

140
00:14:46,552 --> 00:14:49,965
A, Amitabh Bachchan.

141
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,986
Adivinha, Acertaste. Acabas de ganhar 1.000 rupias.

142
00:14:57,035 --> 00:14:58,481
