149
00:15:24,078 --> 00:15:27,262
B: Só as mentiras vencem>>

150
00:15:27,552 --> 00:15:30,122
C: Só a moda vence>>

151
00:15:30,928 --> 00:15:34,531
D: Só o dinheiro vence>>

152
00:15:39,664 --> 00:15:41,465
