223
00:23:49,552 --> 00:23:51,776
B: Tulsidas>>

224
00:23:51,811 --> 00:23:53,608
C: Mira Bai>>

225
00:23:54,038 --> 00:23:56,312
D: Kabir>>

226
00:24:59,000 --> 00:24:59,948
